<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>REPORT_TITLE</title>
    <style media="all" type="text/css">
    html,body{font-family:"Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:.8em;color:#000;background:#fff;margin:0;padding:0;height:100%;overflow-y:auto}
    .hidden-content{display:none;color:#000;text-align:center}
    .flex-row-container{display:flex;flex-direction:row;justify-content:space-between;align-items:stretch;align-content:center}
    .tsc-header{height:60px;background-color:#333;padding:0 15px}
    .tsc-header .title{color:#fff;margin:15px;font-weight:400;align-self:center}
    .tsc-header a{cursor:pointer;align-self:center}
    .tsc-header img{vertical-align:middle;width:24px;height:24px}
    #ts-container{border:0;margin:0;width:100%}
    #ts-container table{font-size:14px;width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:0 auto}
    #ts-container table,th,td{border:1px solid #333;padding:10px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle}
    #ts-container td:nth-child(2){word-wrap:break-word;word-break:break-all}
    #ts-container tr:hover{background-color:#eee}
    #ts-container th{background-color:#ccc}
    #ts-container th:first-child{width:50px;text-align:center}
    #ts-container td:first-child{text-align:center}
    .status-not-started{background-color:gray}
    .status-incomplete{background-color:#f2bc70}
    .fail{background-color:#f19696}
    .icon{height:16px;width:16px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:5px;background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .chrome{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .firefox{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .ie{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .edge{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .remote{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .android{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .ios{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    .headless{background-image:url(data:image/png;base64,)}
    </style>
    <style media="print" type="text/css">
    .no-print,.no-print *{display:none!important}
    .hidden-content{display:block}
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header name="tsc-header" class="tsc-header flex-row-container no-print">
        <div class="flex-row-container">
            <a href="index-frame-view.html" title="Frame View"><img src="data:image/svg+xml;utf8;base64," /></a>
            <h1 class="title">REPORT_TITLE</h1>
        </div>
    </header>
    <h1 class="hidden-content">REPORT_TITLE</h1>
    <div id="ts-container">
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>No.</th>
                    <th>Test Suite ID</th>
                    <th>Environment</th>
                    <th>Status</th>
                    <th>Failed Tests / Total</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody id="ts-table-body"></tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    var tsList = JSON.parse('TEST_SUITE_REPORT_LIST');

    function ready(fn) {
        if (document.readyState != 'loading') {
            fn();
        } else {
            document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', fn);
        }
    }

    ready(function() {
        var tsTableBody = document.getElementById('ts-table-body');
        tsList.forEach(function(item, index) {
            var row = document.createElement('tr');
            row.innerHTML = '<td>' + (index + 1) + '</td><td><a href="' + item.report + '" target="_blank" title="Open report in new window">' + item.id + '</a></td><td><i class="icon ' + item.environment.toLowerCase() + '"></i>' + item.environment + '</td><td style="' + getBackgroundColorStyle(item.status_color) + '">' + item.status + '</td><td style="' + getBackgroundColorStyle(item.fail_color) + '">' + item.fail_on_total + '</td>';
            tsTableBody.appendChild(row);
        });
    });

    function getBackgroundColorStyle(color) {
        if (color === "") {
            return "";
        }
        if (color === "15") {
            color = "lightgray";
        }
        return "background-color: " + color;
    }
    </script>
</body>

</html>
